title: Vaishnavi
subTitle: Born with the divine power, Vaishnavi receives treatment as a goddess by the villagers. After getting killed, she possesses the body of another girl who looks like her to exact revenge for her death.

title: Karishma Kudrat Ka
subTitle: Vijay lives in a village with his family. He makes an enemy with Lala and a bandit, Bhagad, who devises a plan to throw the former out of the village.

title: Ek Aur Bhool Bhulaiyaa
subTitle: Nakulan and his family move into his supposedly haunted ancestral property. However, when his cousin starts behaving uncharacteristically, Nakulan enlists the help of his psychiatrist friend.

title: Keemat: They Are Back
subTitle: Two crooks accidentally kill a man and decide to inform his parents about the bad news. However, once they meet the family, they end up lying to them.

title: Kaun Kare Kurbanie
subTitle: Arjun Singh, a police inspector, lives peacefully with his family in Mumbai, until an alarming case of harassment and murder turns his life upside down.

title: China Gate
subTitle: Colonel Puri requests his former fellow army officers court-martialed in disgrace to redeem themselves by rescuing a village from Jageera, an evil bandit.

title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.

title: Loha
subTitle: After a bid to arrest Sher Singh fails, officer Dayal is crippled and his partner Amar's career is sabotaged. When Amar gets another chance to nab Sher Singh, he hires two crooks for the job.

title: Gambler
subTitle: Though Inspector Dayashanker is lazy, he unwittingly unearths a criminal conspiracy and becomes the pride of his division overnight. However, a local gangsters turn his life into a nightmare.

title: Gambler
subTitle: Though Inspector Dayashanker is lazy, he unwittingly unearths a criminal conspiracy and becomes the pride of his division overnight. However, a local gangsters turn his life into a nightmare.

title: Naach Govinda Naach
subTitle: With dreams of becoming a great dancer, Govinda, an ordinary man, is given the opportunity to compete against Rocky, a celebrated dancer, in a twist of fate.

title: Illaka
subTitle: Two brothers grow up and end up choosing career paths that are polar opposites, one becomes a smuggler and the other a police officer.

title: Kaali Topi Laal Rumaal
subTitle: Commando Vijay arrests a terrorist, Master DD. However, he realises that Master DD is just a pawn and tries to find the real culprit.

title: Hiraasat
subTitle: An honest policeman who lives with his wife and a brother who is a student, gets implicated and arrested in a case of drug-trafficking.

title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Pehchaan
subTitle: Shankar seeks revenge on the judge who convicted him by kidnapping his wife. The judge is unaware of his wife's pregnancy and disowns the child as he thinks she is the result of his wife's infidelity.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Kaise Kahoon Ke Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Karan, a burglar, wishes to permanently leave his profession when he falls in love with Priya. They decide to get married, but Karan finds out that he has cancer.

title: Drishyam
subTitle: When his daughter accidentally kills a man in self-defence, Georgekutty uses his film knowledge to cover it up. Even when the investigation catches up with them, Georgekutty looks out for his family.

title: Josh
subTitle: Set in Vasco, Goa, Max and Prakash are young men who lead two rival groups. Their feud becomes worse when Prakash's brother, Rahul, falls in love with Shirley, Max's twin sister.

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Khudgarz
subTitle: Sita raises her son, Bihari, and his friend Amar as her own and the two treat each other like brothers. However, Amar's father is not too fond of Bihari, and he tries to create a rift between the two.

title: Police Aur Mujrim
subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

title: Baadshah
subTitle: An amateur detective, Raj, goes by the nickname of Baadshah. But this name soon causes a misunderstanding that lands him in the middle of a conspiracy to assassinate the chief minister of Goa.
